@startuml architecturalknowledgedb-primary-sequence
title ArchitecturalKnowledgeDB - Reingest And Context Pack Sequence

actor Maintainer
actor Agent
participant "AKDB CLI / MCP" as Client
participant "ProjectService" as Projects
participant "ImportExportService" as Importer
participant "Repository/Git scanner" as Git
participant "ContextService" as Context
database "SQLite + FTS" as DB
participant "Normative source folders" as Sources <<folder>>
participant "Registered repository" as Repo <<folder>>

Maintainer -> Client : import registry / setup project
Client -> Projects : upsert project + source roots
Projects -> DB : persist project metadata

Maintainer -> Client : reingest project
Client -> Importer : import ADRs, docs, UML
Importer -> Sources : read files
Importer -> DB : upsert knowledge items + FTS
Client -> Git : scan registered repos
Git -> Repo : read git metadata
Git -> DB : store selected provenance

Agent -> Client : get context pack(project, task, paths)
Client -> Context : build_context_pack(...)
Context -> DB : search, rank, load links/provenance
Context --> Client : authority-aware context pack
Client --> Agent : relevant sources + drift/provenance

note over Importer,Sources
  Reingest reads source files and rebuilds derived records.
  It does not write back to Git/docs or Git/UML.
end note

@enduml
